'''Pride Month 2026''' is a community event to celebrate [[Wikipedia:Pride Month|Pride Month]] for 2026. The event featured a pride-themed hub world, a charity fundraising campaign for Trans Lifeline, and several rewards for users participating. It took place from June 1, 2026 - June 30, 2026.

